# Copy this file to `.env` and paste your token (the .env file is gitignored).
# Lichess personal API token — get one at https://lichess.org/account/oauth/token
# (no scopes are required for the Opening Explorer).
#
# BUILD-TIME ONLY: this token is used by `npm run build:stats` to precompute the
# opening win/draw/loss stats into src/data/openings.json. The app itself makes
# NO API calls at runtime, so the token is never shipped in the client bundle.
VITE_LICHESS_TOKEN=
